(488, 74, 'title_2', 'No Obligation, Customized Financial Needs Analysis'),
(489, 74, '_title_2', 'field_5cebe56b4ba32'),
(490, 74, 'text_2', '<h5>Experior Helps You Bring Your Money to Life!</h5>\r\nExperior Financial Group Inc. has Financial Advisors throughout Canada who can assist you in reaching your financial goals. Have one of our highly trained and licensed financial advisors meet with you to assist you with creating a personalized financial pathway that meets your families unique needs and goals. Contact us to arrange a free, no-obligation meeting with Financial Advisor in your area. We\'ll assist you in getting the insurance coverage you need and smart investments that work for you and your unique financial situation.\r\n\r\n<img id=\"comp-jujm76r8__item1imgimage\" class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/5cf5a7_ffdbd48d97a04625958ade05e27764b2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_44,h_44,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/bullet_points_png_191673.webp\" alt=\"bullet_points_png_191673.png\" data-type=\"image\" />Gain an understanding of how to deal with margin erosion.\r\n\r\n<img id=\"comp-jujm76r8__item-jujmijaaimgimage\" class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/5cf5a7_ffdbd48d97a04625958ade05e27764b2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_44,h_44,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/bullet_points_png_191673.webp\" alt=\"bullet_points_png_191673.png\" data-type=\"image\" />Learn how much revenue you can gain by filling portfolio gaps and all billable hours.\r\n\r\n<img id=\"comp-jujm76r8__item-jujmijkiimgimage\" class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/5cf5a7_ffdbd48d97a04625958ade05e27764b2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_44,h_44,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/bullet_points_png_191673.webp\" alt=\"bullet_points_png_191673.png\" data-type=\"image\" />Evaluate and strategize a positive impact on EBIDTA.\r\n\r\n<img id=\"comp-jujm76r8__item-jujmijtbimgimage\" class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/5cf5a7_ffdbd48d97a04625958ade05e27764b2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_44,h_44,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/bullet_points_png_191673.webp\" alt=\"bullet_points_png_191673.png\" data-type=\"image\" />Risk analyses for 5 types of pitfalls for implementations of scaling and cost optimizations.\r\n\r\n<img id=\"comp-jujm76r8__item-j9pnv9cmimgimage\" class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/5cf5a7_ffdbd48d97a04625958ade05e27764b2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_44,h_44,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/bullet_points_png_191673.webp\" alt=\"bullet_points_png_191673.png\" data-type=\"image\" />High-precision model of cost savings for the next 2-years. Includes 8 major type of cost savings.\r\n\r\n<img id=\"comp-jujm76r8__item-jujsum55imgimage\" class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/5cf5a7_ffdbd48d97a04625958ade05e27764b2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_44,h_44,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/bullet_points_png_191673.webp\" alt=\"bullet_points_png_191673.png\" data-type=\"image\" />Simple Strategies Technology Service Providers can leverage to grow their business in new markets, verticals or just to grow their bottom-line\r\n\r\n<img id=\"comp-jujm76r8__item-jujsun3oimgimage\" class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/5cf5a7_ffdbd48d97a04625958ade05e27764b2~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_44,h_44,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/bullet_points_png_191673.webp\" alt=\"bullet_points_png_191673.png\" data-type=\"image\" />Detailed example of roadmap to success for first 3 months with projected days and savings.'),
