(502, 74, 'title_4', 'About Us'),
(503, 74, '_title_4', 'field_5ced13218a572'),
(504, 74, 'text_4', 'Established in 2014, with our Headquarters in Guelph, Ontario and Financial Advisors throughout Canada. Our Motto is Building financial foundations for families to empower them today and leave a legacy for tomorrow.'),
(505, 74, '_text_4', 'field_5ced13518a574'),
(506, 74, 'items_0_title', 'Licensed Financial Advisors'),
(507, 74, '_items_0_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(508, 74, 'items_0_text', 'Established in 2014, our 1100+ team of well trained and provincially licensed Financial Advisors are available across Canada to assist you with all of your insurance and investment needs. Our Financial Advisors appreciate the ongoing training and support they receive throughout their financial services career with Experior Financial Group.'),
(509, 74, '_items_0_text', 'field_5ced15418a57b'),
(510, 74, 'items_0_img', '73'),
(511, 74, '_items_0_img', 'field_5ced16188a57e'),
(512, 74, 'items_1_title', 'Years Of Experience'),
(513, 74, '_items_1_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(514, 74, 'items_1_text', 'Headquartered in Guelph, Ontario Canada. Our founders Jamie and Lee-Ann Prickett built Experior Financial Group and shared over 25+ years between them in the financial services industry. Our Experior Financial Group Executives boast well over 150+ years in the financial services industry. Experior Financial Advisors receive a high level of training, ongoing support and mentoring from our hands on Executive Leaders ensuring that our financial service clients receive superior solutions.'),
(515, 74, '_items_1_text', 'field_5ced15418a57b'),
(516, 74, 'items_1_img', '72'),
(517, 74, '_items_1_img', 'field_5ced16188a57e'),
(518, 74, 'items_2_title', 'Best Of The Best'),
(519, 74, '_items_2_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(520, 74, 'items_2_text', 'Experior Financial Group offers a unique Tribrid model. We took the best of the captive, networking and brokering world to create a unique Managing General Agency (MGA) offering only the best tools, support and benefits for both our clients and our financial advisors. We have become known across the country as one of the fastest growing MGA\'s in Canada for these reasons.'),
