(588, 79, 'items_0_title', 'Why Experior'),
(589, 79, '_items_0_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(590, 79, 'items_0_text', 'Our goal at Experior Financial Group is to help our clients reach their financial goals. As a Canadian owned an operated company you can be assured that we work hard to help get you on the right financial pathway. Recognizing that every individual and family will have unique financial goals we work with you to create a pathway to achieving your financial goals. We offer Debt help, Life Insurance, Critical illness insurance, Term insurance, Investments and so much more.'),
