(629, 79, '_items_3_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(630, 79, 'items_3_text', 'We are pleased to have financial services offices located across Canada to serve our clients and advisors with their insurance and investment needs. Please continue here for a list of offices and contact information nearest to your area or send us your information and we\'ll see that one of our Expert Financial Advisors reaches out to you.'),
