(786, 101, 'text_4', ''),
(787, 101, '_text_4', 'field_5ced13518a574'),
(788, 101, 'items_0_title', 'Why Experior'),
(789, 101, '_items_0_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(790, 101, 'items_0_text', 'Our goal at Experior Financial Group is to help our clients reach their financial goals. As a Canadian owned an operated company you can be assured that we work hard to help get you on the right financial pathway. Recognizing that every individual and family will have unique financial goals we work with you to create a pathway to achieving your financial goals. We offer Debt help, Life Insurance, Critical illness insurance, Term insurance, Investments and so much more.'),
(791, 101, '_items_0_text', 'field_5ced15418a57b'),
(792, 101, 'items_0_img', '75'),
(793, 101, '_items_0_img', 'field_5ced16188a57e'),
(794, 101, 'items_1_title', 'About Us'),
(795, 101, '_items_1_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(796, 101, 'items_1_text', 'Experior Financial Group is a Managing General Agency (MGA). We train, support, mentor and assist our Financial Advisors in getting clients the absolute best products and investment tools. Established in 2014, we\'ve grown to over 750+ Advisors all across Canada and have more than 12 offices to serve you. Our company was built by Advisors, and that is why so many Advisors and Associate General Agencies have chosen Experior to be their home for everything they need to have a successful financial advisor career in the Financial Services industry.'),
(797, 101, '_items_1_text', 'field_5ced15418a57b'),
(798, 101, 'items_1_img', '76'),
(799, 101, '_items_1_img', 'field_5ced16188a57e'),
(800, 101, 'items_2_title', 'Careers'),
(801, 101, '_items_2_title', 'field_5ced15ff8a57d'),
(802, 101, 'items_2_text', 'Experior Financial Group offers back-office support, mentoring, ongoing training both online and in person. As one of the fastest growing Managing General Agencies (MGA) in Canada both Financial Advisors and Associated General Agencies (AGA) are choosing Experior Financial Group to be the best fit. You may be a seasoned financial services professional or are just starting in the financial services industry. Experior has everything you need to get you well on your way to building your business or Associated General Agency (AGA). Find out more.'),
